                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَعْلُوا عَلَى﴾ تَتَكَبَّرُوا عَلَيَّ.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
